		<dc:creator><![CDATA[未曾]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 28 Aug 2023 23:00:38 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.shuge.org/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=108032</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<img width="710" height="375" src="https://txcdn.shuge.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/hai_zhen_tu_juan10-710x375.jpg" class="attachment-magazine size-magazine wp-post-image" alt="海珍图卷" decoding="async" style="margin-bottom:10px;" />此《海珍图》卷由南宋刘松年绘。画卷以艳丽的色彩表现画家所了解或臆想的海洋生物，描绘了蚌蛤、螺贝、海龟、海猪、蟹、鲎、珊瑚等三十一种。每种右侧用金粉书写四字题名，如：海蓑云月、合擎蚌蛤、云球簇海、海际玉蟾、海猪拜月、玉芝翠管等等。此卷现藏于台北故宫博物院。]]></description>
		
